pulltitle: makes list-detail template work in firefox Aurora/Nightly
pullsbody:
FIxes issue 4 of css-animations ('insertRule doesn't exist in W3C CSSKeyframesRule interface'). See https://github.com/jlongster/css-animations.js/issues/4

The pull request applies the orignal fix of jlongster on the mortar-list-detail repo: 
https://github.com/jlongster/css-animations.js/commit/bedeff09f1e716f8fab5879d385397b0e511ad77
pull_repo_desc: A list detail view template for an Open Web App.
pull_commit_message:
detect usage of appendRule instead of insertRule

applied fix of orginal repo: https://github.com/jlongster/css-animations.js/commit/bedeff09f1e716f8fab5879d385397b0e511ad77

pulltitle: Fix setting titleField on a listView
pullsbody:
Setting a title field on a listView doesn't work because it uses 'opts' instead of 'options'. This patch fixes that.

I have also submitted a pull request to the upstream mozilla/mortar-layouts repo.
pull_repo_desc: A list detail view template for an Open Web App.
pull_commit_message: Fix to use proper option member.
